## Batch-approval receipt schema (`ghtf:ApprovalBatch` — vocabulary + doc only)

| property | meaning |
|---|---|
| `ghtf:repoSet` | multi: the repos this batch authorizes, by `ghtf:repoIdentity` |
| `ghtf:perRepoPlanDigest` | multi: `repo=digest` of each repo's individual plan |
| `ghtf:aggregatePlanDigest` | digest over the ordered per-repo plan digests |
| `ghtf:riskTier` | the highest tier touched by the batch |
| `ghtf:authorizedBy` | the human/role who authorized the batch |
| `ghtf:expiry` | after this instant the batch authorizes nothing |
| `ghtf:maxMutations` | refuse if the applied mutation count would exceed this |
| `ghtf:zeroDeleteCondition` | condition under which any delete voids the batch |

No apply path consumes this schema yet — Phase 2 declares the vocabulary only.

